node.text:
Which of these colorful birds is your favorite? 😍 From 1 to 10? 🦜🎨 You can check how to get your photos promoted in our account, use the link in our bio @tripfever

Names and Photos: 
1. Silver throated Tanager @jeffreypatrickkarnes
2. European Starling @raheel.aazim
3. Mandarin duck @eccentricwildlife
4. Golden-tailed Sapphire @birddetective
5. Strawberry Finch @praharsha_wildlife_stories
6. Periquito-rico @macrotake
7. European Bee-eater @dorugroza
8. Pink Robin @ravi_arora
9. Keel billed Toucan @floriankusterwildlife
10. Oriental Dwarf Kingfisher @rahul_belsare

node.text:
Hiking goals 😍🐕 You can check how to get your photos promoted in our account, use the link in our bio @tripfever

With @gossegoss and @varvik in Geiranger, one of the most spectacular @nature destinations in Norway.

"We ended up having Skageflå—which is one of the most popular hikes—all to ourselves. Videos and pictures will never do this place justice though, and it is popular for a reason! I just can’t believe how lucky we got. 🍃"

If you're looking for a breathtaking sight to explore the fiords, this is it! Tag someone you would take for a @nature-filled getaway in Norway with! 🇳🇴

📽 @varvik
🚶🏼‍♀️@gossegoss
🐶 @roamingpuppers
📍 Skageflå, Geiranger, Norway
🎶 What A Wonderful World - Louis Armstrong
